E!',12,7,100,0,0,0,'Inquisitor Hallard'),(27316,9,0,'LET THE LIGHT IN, GODFREY GOODARD!',12,7,100,0,0,0,'Inquisitor Hallard'),(27316,10,0,'May the power of Light compel you!',12,7,100,0,0,0,'Inquisitor Hallard'),(27316,11,0,'I thought you would see the Light, Godfrey... Now speak quickly, fiend. What does it say?',12,7,100,396,0,0,'Inquisitor Hallard'),(27316,12,0,'RUBBISH! Godfrey do you take me for a fool? Do not spew your Scourge propaganda at a man of the Light, heathen! Speak now or I will have the peasants craft a holy water bath and dip you into it like a dog with fleas!',12,7,100,6,0,0,'Inquisitor Hallard'),(27316,13,0,'What? There is a mausoleum beneath the old village? What fools we are to not have noticed! We will find and strike down your master now, Godfrey. We will end this nightmare.',12,7,100,6,0,0,'Inquisitor Hallard'),(27316,14,0,'You let us worry about how we kill the monster, Godfrey.',12,7,100,396,0,0,'Inquisitor Hallard'),(27316,15,0,'Return to Halford with the information that the good mayor was kind enough to submit, $N. I will finish here and squeeze whatever else this wretch might know about Thel\'zan. Now, I will show Godfrey the rarely seen \"option three.\"',12,7,100,1,0,0,'Inquisitor Hallard'),(27316,16,0,'Let\'s you and I have a chat about some things, Godfrey.',12,7,100,1,0,0,'Inquisitor Hallard'),(27447,0,0,'There will be no mercy!',14,0,0,0,0,13649,''),(27447,1,1,'Blast them! Destroy them!',14,0,0,0,0,13650,''),(27447,2,2,'%s calls an Azure Ring Captain!',41,0,0,0,0,0,''),(27447,3,3,'They are... too strong! Underestimated their... fortitude.',14,0,0,0,0,13655,''),(27577,0,0,'%s growls.',16,0,100,0,0,409,'Mayor Godfrey'),(27577,1,0,'%s hisses!',16,0,100,0,0,410,'Mayor Godfrey'),(27577,2,0,'Tell you nothing, preacher.',12,0,100,1,0,0,'Mayor Godfrey'),(27577,3,0,'What can you do to me that Kel\'Thuzad has not? That the Lich King will not?',12,0,100,1,0,0,'Mayor Godfrey'),(27577,4,0,'The book is your salvation, yes... but nothing will you know! NOTHING I SAY! NOTHING! ',12,0,100,1,0,0,'Mayor Godfrey'),(27577,5,0,'No more LIGHT! NO MORE! I BEG YOU!',12,0,100,0,0,0,'Mayor Godfrey'),(27577,6,0,'Never felt hurt like this!',12,0,100,0,0,0,'Mayor Godfrey'),(27577,7,0,'It tells of the coming apocalypse. How this world will burn and be reborn from death.',12,0,100,1,0,0,'Mayor Godfrey'),(27577,8,0,'NOOOO!!! I tell you! I tell you everything!',12,0,100,39,0,0,'Mayor Godfrey'),(27577,9,0,'Humans... Beneath the earth of Wintergarde Village you built a mausoleum! Why do you think Naxxramas attacked that spot? Thel\'zan hides deep in your own crypt and sends a thousand-thousand corpses at you! Perish you will...',12,0,100,1,0,0,'Mayor Godfrey'),(27577,10,0,'How? Humans truly are stupid, yes? Thel\'zan the Duskbringer! Thel\'zan the Lich! He who is born of human flesh and bone, sacrificed all for power, protected by the Lich King!',12,0,100,1,0,0,'Mayor Godfrey'),(27577,11,0,'You cannot stop Thel\'zan! He bears the dark gift, bestowed upon him by the Lich King himself!',12,0,100,1,0,0,'Mayor Godfrey'),(27656,0,0,'You brash interlopers are out of your element! I will ground you!',14,0,0,0,0,0,'Boss Eregos - Aggro'),(27656,1,0,'Such insolence... such arrogance... must be PUNISHED!',14,0,0,0,0,0,'Boss Eregos - Enrage'),(27656,2,0,'Savor this small victory, foolish little creatures. You and your dragon allies have won this battle. But we will win... the Nexus War.',14,0,0,0,0,0,'Boss Eregos - Death'),(27842,0,0,'Bat gizzards again for the gnomes tonight...',12,0,100,1,0,0,'Fenrick Barlowe text'),(27842,0,1,'What do they expect, making the bats come in at that angle? Broken necks and gamey bat stew, that\'s what they get.',12,0,100,1,0,0,'Fenrick Barlowe text'),(27842,0,2,'We like trees, Fenrick. They provide cover. They won\'t let me chop them down, either.',12,0,100,1,0,0,'Fenrick Barlowe text'),(27842,0,3,'I wonder how many reinforcements need to suffer injury before they allows us to chop down these idiotic tree